      <h2>Finding people has never been this easy!</h2>
      <p>Let's say you want to go to a concert, but you have no one to go with.<br>
        Or maybe you saw someone interesting but were too shy to talk to them.</p>
      <p>All you have to do is make a post, and anyone interested can <em>apply</em>. Then you'll be able to connect!</p>
      <p>Posts can be anonymous and are organized in <em>communities</em>.</p>
      <p>You'll only see posts from communities you are subscribed to. To subscribe to a community, just visit the <em>communities</em> page and start looking for the ones you are interested in! (e.g. your school, city, hobby, etc.). You can subscribe to as many communities as you like.</p>
      <p>Posts look like this:</p>
      <div class="post"><div class="titlebar"><p class="title username title_ext">johnsmith</p><p class="title post_community">@nyc</p><p class="title date"><time>3 h</time></p><div class="dotdotdot_wrap"><svg class="dotdotdot_post" width="40px" height="40px" viewBox="-2 -5 28 28"><path d="m12 16.495c1.242 0 2.25 1.008 2.25 2.25s-1.008 2.25-2.25 2.25-2.25-1.008-2.25-2.25 1.008-2.25 2.25-2.25zm0-6.75c1.242 0 2.25 1.008 2.25 2.25s-1.008 2.25-2.25 2.25-2.25-1.008-2.25-2.25 1.008-2.25 2.25-2.25zm0-6.75c1.242 0 2.25 1.008 2.25 2.25s-1.008 2.25-2.25 2.25-2.25-1.008-2.25-2.25 1.008-2.25 2.25-2.25z"></path></svg></div></div><p class="postcontent">Looking for someone to go out with this saturday night! My friends are all busy :(</p><div class="postbar"><div class="likes unliked"><span class="likecount">47</span><svg class="likeicon" width="40px" height="40px" viewBox="-2 -3 28 28"><path d="M12 4.435c-1.989-5.399-12-4.597-12 3.568 0 4.068 3.06 9.481 12 14.997 8.94-5.516 12-10.929 12-14.997 0-8.118-10-8.999-12-3.568z"></path></svg></div><div class="ncomments showcomments"><span class="commcount">6</span><svg class="commicon" width="40px" height="40px" viewBox="-2 -3 28 28"><path d="M12 1c-6.628 0-12 4.573-12 10.213 0 2.39.932 4.591 2.427 6.164l-2.427 5.623 7.563-2.26c9.495 2.598 16.437-3.251 16.437-9.527 0-5.64-5.372-10.213-12-10.213z"></path></svg></div><div class="apply_button unapplied"><span class="applycount">10</span><svg class="appicon" width="40px" height="40px" viewBox="-2 -2 28 28"><path d="M12 .587l3.668 7.568 8.332 1.151-6.064 5.828 1.48 8.279-7.416-3.967-7.417 3.967 1.481-8.279-6.064-5.828 8.332-1.151z"></path></svg></div></div></div>
      <p>You can interact with posts in different ways:</p>
          <div class = "action"><div class="likes unliked"><svg class="likeicon" width="40px" height="40px" viewBox="-2 -3 28 28"><path d="M12 4.435c-1.989-5.399-12-4.597-12 3.568 0 4.068 3.06 9.481 12 14.997 8.94-5.516 12-10.929 12-14.997 0-8.118-10-8.999-12-3.568z"></path></svg></div><p><em>Like</em>: liking a post is completely anonymous and will just boost the post so that it can reach more people.</p></div>
          <div class = "action"><div class="ncomments showcomments"><svg class="commicon" width="40px" height="40px" viewBox="-2 -3 28 28"><path d="M12 1c-6.628 0-12 4.573-12 10.213 0 2.39.932 4.591 2.427 6.164l-2.427 5.623 7.563-2.26c9.495 2.598 16.437-3.251 16.437-9.527 0-5.64-5.372-10.213-12-10.213z"></path></svg></div><p><em>Comment</em>: comment to share your thoughts about the post! Everyone can see comments.</p></div>
          <div class = "action"><div class="apply_button unapplied"><svg class="appicon" width="40px" height="40px" viewBox="-2 -2 28 28"><path d="M12 .587l3.668 7.568 8.332 1.151-6.064 5.828 1.48 8.279-7.416-3.967-7.417 3.967 1.481-8.279-6.064-5.828 8.332-1.151z"></path></svg></div><p><em>Apply</em>: the most important feature, it lets you connect directly with the person who made the post!</p></div>
      <p>If you send a post, you can see who applied to it by clicking on the star icon, and you can choose who you want to accept.</p>
      <p>Once you accept someone, you will be able to chat with them on the <em>messages</em> page.</p>
      <p>To use Spotted, create an account and fill in your profile so others can get to know you.</p>
      <h2>What are you waiting for!</h2>
